{"service_name": ".HTG Disaster Recovery Design and Strategy", "service_id": "7390848281428356", "company_name": "Howell Technology Group Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Howell Technology Group Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     .HTG Disaster Recovery Design and Strategy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Considering Cloud design as the future of scalable distributed IT this service considers Business Continuity and Availability requirements. Understanding of Single Point of Failure and Capacity Shortfall, value is added by potential issue identification and mitigation of the risk each introduces through review, documentation, redesign and development.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Policies and Procedures Review, risk understanding\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Resilience, Redundancy and High Availability Review, risk understanding\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity impact assessment, risk understanding\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Disaster Scenario simulation, qualification and impact quantification\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Architectural Gap Analysis\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Business Availabilty Risk Understanding, through Gap Anaysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity Risk Mitigation, through Policy and Procedure Redesign\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Continuous Improvement towards Three Nines Plus availability\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity and Availability Deployment Planning\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3450 to \u00a3950 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700102/7390848281428356-pricing-document-2015-10-02-1254.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700102/7390848281428356-service-definition-document-2015-10-02-1254.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700102/7390848281428356-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-02-1254.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vii\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 7\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"serv